item.title: About Me
item.description: Hello, I’m Alan. I have around 4 years of experience as a software engineer and focus on back-end. In my free time, I passionately love learning new knowledge which can make me think better and comprehensively to solve problems or create value. I hope that my passion can create more products that users love and use. Experience Higgs • Full Stack Enginner • Apr. 2018 ~ Present ISCOM Online International Information Inc • Software Engineer • Seo.
